message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed to meet your needs. With its exceptional features and quality, it's truly a valuable asset. Considering its worth and the benefits it offers, I propose a price of $125 for you to experience all it has to provide. I believe this offer strikes a fair balance between value and cost, making it an attractive opportunity for you. Please let me know if you're interested in proceeding with this offer.
